_sText: Gg_trainyard ------------ About: One of my most time consuming maps made to date. A newly abandoned trainstation lies in the center of the map. With multiple ways to enter or avoid the station. Rail road tracks are positioned just outside each teams spawn. Teams can go either around, into the building, or camp their tracks. ------------ Other Info: 32 Slot Recommended 4v4+ Soundscape (train.outside) Buyzones (If needed) Pure-Awesomeness included. ------------ Notes: Enjoy Tom_Tom P.S. please don't edit without prior permission. Like my work? See more at... tom_tom92's Maplist
